# AI Framework - Minimal .gitignore
# Only framework-specific rules. Add your project rules below.

/.claude
/CLAUDE.md
/hooks/*.db
/hooks/__pycache__/

# Ralph orchestrator (operational, per-objective) — keep specs + scenarios tracked
/.ralph/*
!/.ralph/specs/
!/.ralph/specs/**

# Deep research artifacts (per-investigation)
/.research/

# Brainstorming session files (mockups, server state)
/.brainstorm/

# Visual companion session files (frontend-design mockups)
/.visual-companion/

# Specs and planning artifacts — keep tracked under /docs/specs and
# /.ralph/specs (un-ignored above) so the scenarios contract committed
# under either discovery root is bisectable. The legacy /.claude/scenarios/
# allowlist is removed: that path is no longer the discovery root.
!/docs/specs/
!/docs/specs/**
/.claude/metrics.jsonl
/.claude/metrics.jsonl.*

# AI Framework runtime files (auto-added)
/.claude/*
!/.claude/rules/
.brainstorm/
